r%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EEvery%20tip%20is%20treated%20with%20care%2C%20but%20not%20every%20submission%20can%20be%20investigated.%20Please%20understand%20that%20we%20cannot%20guarantee%20a%20response%20or%20publication%20of%20every%20disclosure.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELegal%20Notice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EOfficial%20Secrets%20Act%201989%3A%20If%20you%20are%20bound%20by%20the%20Act%2C%20disclosing%20certain%20categories%20of%20information%20(defence%2C%20security%2C%20intelligence%2C%20international%20relations)%20is%20a%20criminal%20offence.%20There%20is%20no%20public%20interest%20defence.%20Restore%20Britain%20cannot%20protect%20you%20from%20prosecution%20under%20this%20Act.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EConfidentiality%20%26amp%3B%20contracts%3A%20If%20you%20are%20bound%20by%20an%20employment%20contract%20or%20confidentiality%20agreement%2C%20disclosure%20may%20expose%20you%20to%20civil%20or%20criminal%20liability.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EWe%20cannot%20give%20legal%20advice.%20If%20you%20are%20uncertain%2C%20please%20seek%20independent%20legal%20advice%20before%20submitting.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EIf%20you%20ever%20believe%20you%20are%20in%20immediate%20danger%20before%2C%20during%2C%20or%20after%20making%20a%20disclosure%2C%20call%20the%20police%20or%20emergency%20services.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20Protection%20and%20Your%20Rights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3EWe%20comply%20with%20UK%20GDPR%20and%20the%20Data%20Protection%20Act%202018%2C%20applying%20the%20journalism%20exemption%20where%20appropriate.%20This%20means%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EYour%20personal%20data%20is%20only%20processed%20where%20necessary%20for%20journalism%20in%20the%20public%20interest.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EWe%20minimise%20what%20we%20collect%2C%20keep%20it%20encrypted%2C%20and%20delete%20it%20when%20no%20longer%20required.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EYou%20have%20the%20right%20to%20object%20to%20processing%20of%20your%20personal%20data.%20All%20complaints%20are%20logged%2C%20reviewed%2C%20and%20assessed%20fairly.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%22Whistleblower%20Privacy%20%26amp%3B%20Protection%20Policy%22%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fassets.nationbuilder.com%2Frestorebritain%2Fpages%2F530%2Fattachments%2Foriginal%2F1765191445%2FWhistleblower_Privacy___Protection_Policy.pdf%3F1765191445%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20our%20full%20Whistleblower%20Privacy%20%26amp%3B%20Protection%20Policy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Blow%20the%20Whistle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3EWe%20use%20a%20tiered%20system%20depending%20on%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20your%20information%2C%20for%20Tiers%202%20%26amp%3B%203%20please%20download%20the%20Whistleblower%20Guide%20Pack%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20page%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETier%201%20%E2%80%94%20Low%20Sensitivity%20(General%20leads)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EUse%20our%20submission%20link%20for%20non-sensitive%20tips.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EDo%20not%20upload%20confidential%2C%20personal%2C%20or%20classified%20documents.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3Cli%3EBest%20for%3A%20public%20material%2C%20small%20leads%2C%20or%20starting%20a%20conversation.%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3EYou%20can%20fill%20out%20the%20form%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Frestorebritain.typeform.com%2Fwhistleblowing%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20style%3D%22font-weight%3A%20400%3B%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETier%202%20%E2%80%94%20Medium%20Sensitivity%20(Private%20e